 when I hear \"Whites are just jealous of our culture\" from the same people that refuse to maintain their own property and wear airbrushed ill fitting memorial shirts for various  friends and family who were murdered by their own people before they were 20 years old.", "last_comment_created": 1781492026283, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 5, "score_up": 45, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASss0nwP3", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 214, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8679871, "raw_content": "Even state and local elections cannot be treated as purely internal matters. When states effectively conduct de facto foreign aid by harboring illegal immigrants\u2014providing them sanctuary, benefits, and services\u2014while including non-citizens in the census count, they distort federal apportionment of House seats, Electoral College votes, and billions in federal funding. This shifts political power and resources away from American citizens nationwide, making every state\u2019s election integrity a legitimate concern for the entire country.", "author": "MemoryHoleyeO", "created": 1781455986037, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Rango", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "All elections have turned into a federal matter because the harboring of foreigners and feigning it as aid. Every American is dis